33	/**
34	 * Community posts + comments. Visibility model: every post belongs to an org,
35	 * and reads are scope-filtered. {@code PUBLIC} posts are returned to admin
36	 * users globally; org-scoped users see the union of PUBLIC posts in their orgs
37	 * and any ORGANIZATION posts in their orgs. Hidden and deleted posts are not
38	 * returned to normal reads — they remain visible to moderation workflows via
39	 * {@link ModerationService}.
40	 *
41	 * <p>Phase C8 extensions:
42	 * <ul>
43	 *   <li>threaded replies and quote-replies on comments</li>
44	 *   <li>likes on posts and comments (idempotent insert + hard-delete unlike)</li>
45	 *   <li>follow / unfollow between users</li>
46	 *   <li>{@code @username} mention parsing with notification delivery</li>
47	 *   <li>thread-mute and user-block with feed filtering</li>
48	 * </ul>
49	 * Notifications for replies, mentions, likes, and follows are delivered
50	 * inline in the same transaction so a failed notification rolls the whole
51	 * interaction back — keeping the audit trail consistent with the state.
52	 */
53	@Service
54	public class CommunityService {
