281	    /**
282	     * Return the canonical CSV template content for student bulk imports.
283	     * Controller serves this as {@code text/csv} so operators can download a
284	     * pre-filled header row, fill it in offline, and upload it back. The
285	     * template header is kept in lock-step with the parser via
286	     * {@link #IMPORT_TEMPLATE_HEADERS}.
